ateForm()\n\t{\n\t\tvar f = document.frmlogin;\n\t\tif(f.member_username.value=='')\n\t\t{\n\t\t\talert('Please enter the Username.');\n\t\t\tf.member_username.focus(); return false;\n\t\t}\n\t\tif(f.member_password.value=='')\n\t\t{\n\t\t\talert('Please specify the Password.');\n\t\t\tf.member_password.focus(); return false;\n\t\t}\n\t}\n\t//]]\u003e\n\u003c/script\u003e\n```\n### PoC Attached is the html code: {F175917}\n\n### Impact:\n* An attacker can Brute force their password.\n* Brute force Attack\n\n\nRegards,\nj3","weakness":{"id":45,"name":"Cross-Site Request Forgery (CSRF)"},"original_report_id":null,"original_report_url":null,"attachments":[{"id":175917,"file_name":"csrf_token_is_missing.html","expiring_url":"https://hackerone-us-west-2-production-attachments.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/000/175/917/9665dc0dc8b938426d70c3281bff8bc6301f04a4/csrf_token_is_missing.html?response-content-disposition=attachment%3B%20filename%3D%22csrf_token_is_missing.html%22%3B%20filename%2A%3DUTF-8%27%27csrf_token_is_missing.html\u0026response-content-type=application%2Foctet-stream\u0026X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256\u0026X-Amz-Credential=ASIAQGK6FURQQHFIXVG3%2F20260429%2Fus-west-2%2Fs3%2Faws4_request\u0026X-Amz-Date=20260429T103040Z\u0026X-Amz-Expires=3600\u0026X-Amz-Security-Token=IQoJb3JpZ2luX2VjECkaCXVzLXdlc3QtMiJHMEUCIE02P0ymQp7XsGcUysuhXUZrw7nLLFHmSG%2BuZBmZEELPAiEA8OYF9%2FlSMvfS6b71uFtYixWqyv2FWthOgNF9F8CpzOUquwUI8v%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2FARADGgwwMTM2MTkyNzQ4NDkiDM67gtjsF3tU1qLhcCqPBcuzTMk0DmXt1cERCQ2LIzE9bCn39DzFXvJln1g%2FGYXE55jS%2B2%2BFzH%2B7aw3EfmypyyKQRxhPx8FYFJl4qHq9279jDtSt1fSKEmbToMsj674pM0u8It02wGLeuN8CKYGpoOBr6MHcxutM4sIjaLlEdMsAZJYzl2OjKAEXBVPkUhHGxrb4AM%2FDFw2ZYrQuQERHreNvf0xWV1UZhfIud%2B%2BFeIh3IlSNTLH9pMkveu9vso2bDplq6Oq9%2Fuq1WWXCL52FI2DDDZVsRJzWTqaH2vTOfyaGBdiZcdCgwjKEy0wyCeYJXw2TroV2kS6rLKYZQSV5tHGgTRo4P3qtPh9YomABAMDpN1Pf%2B921Hr6kU8lRUPckucgo%2BOfNEGBMPaiPaHd%2BAQDyqwItepil0QLnbuZW907p4MIhb%2BaVvEiYzlv1kp65gL%2BnkFciCwHwyHbrJkkgOdejaW1SgdEIA4